好係遊水，其次踩單車，受傷機會低啲。<br />\n做咩運動都可以減肥，最重要搵一樣你鐘意既，最好可以日日做既運動。<br />\n初初隔日做30分鐘，當你覺得力量大咗可以加長時間，先建立好基本耐力。<br />\n配合飲食，戒糖，減少 carbohydrate，多食蔬果多飲水，每日訓番6-8個鐘。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"打籃球ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023747dcbd4baeffc9cfcb7547c21c50cdcae2e9","tid":734332,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7148fd2e38a3a57973496ccc0721b89547482cbb","tid":734332,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81c521b1074e94e3028d53efab87e651da47722","tid":734332,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03620454a5366a0f220cd76b9499e2962b1aedb7","tid":734332,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"巴<br />\n<br />\n178<br />\n<br />\n90<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"你個磅數最好係遊水，其次踩單車，受傷機會低啲。<br />\n做咩運動都可以減肥，最重要搵一樣你鐘意既，最好可以日日做既運動。<br />\n初初隔日做30分鐘，當你覺得力量大咗可以加長時間，先建立好基本耐力。<br />\n配合飲食，戒糖，減少 carbohydrate，多食蔬果多飲水，每日訓番6-8個鐘。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"打籃球ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"可以呀，不過要睇點樣打法，運動既強度決定減得有幾快。<br />\n如果係正式球隊操練，或者成日打比賽既既高強度運動，都會減得好快。<br />\n如果只係練射波，就比較難減到了。<br />\n<br />\n你可以參考下呢類片，好多基本動作都可以減到肥，亦針對藍球上所需。<br />\n<a href=\"https:/